M. Troy Woods



Mr. M. T. Woods is Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at Total System Services, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at China UnionPay Data Co. Ltd., GP Network Corp., Greater Columbus Chamber of Commerce, YMCA of Metropolitan Columbus, Columbus State University and Rivercenter for the Performing Arts. Mr. Woods was previously employed as Senior Vice President-Consumer Lending by AmSouth Bank of Alabama and Vice President by Columbus Bank & Trust Co. (Columbus, Georgia). He also served on the board at West Georgia Honor Flight Hub. He received his undergraduate degree from Columbus State University, an undergraduate degree from the University of Virginia and an undergraduate degree from Graduate School of Banking at Louisiana State University.



