M. Troy Woods 
Executive Compensation
As Chairman and Chief Executive Officer at TOTAL SYSTEM SERVICES INC, M. Troy Woods  made $6,399,292 in total compensation.  Of this total $869,000 was received as a salary, $1,789,600 was received as a bonus, $1,233,609 was received in stock options, $2,361,354 was awarded as stock and $145,729 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


